Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫 烫烫烫烫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 大家来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副得意相让我们吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 对…对不起 我觉得有点冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样 让人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波个头最大 给最大的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说波波个头最大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我变大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 很好吃哦 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我[最]怎么样的呢 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集的话 给葡萄干最多的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你直接告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我吧 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸 纸  还有笔 给
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个表达面麻的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不能写 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明日记上就能写… 给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是没有墨了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次 再让我试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见子 好痛苦 鹤见子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉现在好困
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 一股脱力感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻并没有生我们的气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是原谅我们了还不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果生气的话 不会做蒸面包的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:04:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能正是因为无法原谅 为了责备我们才出现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话…话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然能写字的话 一开始就写出来不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能交谈 马上就能相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳和面麻都太迟钝了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是相信面麻的存在 其实是想独占面麻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好打工攒钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对把烟花做出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定 一定要让面麻成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹腾成那样 一定累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起做烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让你能成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你高兴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还醒着么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 乱跑的话会很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻在跑 我也要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳… 无法原谅喜欢仁碳的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周能和我换班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换班？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周四桥梁那边有施工 日薪很高 准备去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算厌倦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说… 我说 对面有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子的母亲和山先生联络过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 伯母她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么并不是叔叔您反对做烟花吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还活在过去里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子出了事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那时起时间就停滞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望让她回到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 请不要再让她回忆起过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松雪君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说有点大言不惭但是我能理解伯母的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对您女儿… 我喜欢芽衣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想为芽衣子做些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也是生活在过去中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然做这么逊的事情让我吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没有变呢 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了面麻什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信的话就可以吗 让面麻成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么执着于面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过宿海的话就能对话了吧 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过宿海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来打工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天会晚点了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前送面麻回家先
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么不想呆在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论到哪里都跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 想和大家一起加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说想和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发还那么长吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是和我们一样成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成长？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会喜欢这个丑女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该算是吧 可爱系？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本来就算是而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就像是看独角戏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 其实不是这样吧 因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集崩坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九话 大家和面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 教你们做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花 烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能让你们碰火药
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是简单的打下手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吓人啊  你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 这是要从竹筒里出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得红色多一点比较可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱？真是和你的形象不符
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 在这里点火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比较容易搬到发射台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}好厉害 好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 面麻 好危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放开啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 做好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在她跳到你的背上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 面麻 饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 波波 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见面麻却又能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是过去还是现在都赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我去把橙汁买来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你跑开了 我也得以逃开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻就在旁边 这让我很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却看不到面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连说话都不能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想再次见到面麻 但为何只有宿海能见到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为是宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海也是心里只有面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时没有一点改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承认失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都喊他仁碳了 却又立即改口叫宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛呀 摆出一副把一切都看透的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看透的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫同类人的共鸣么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你这种品质恶劣的人同类 绝对不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前说过的那些 我是相当认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说咱俩试着交往下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是对男人没耐性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮一踢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 什么漂亮一踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么笑 我是真的大吃一惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于那么吃惊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我开始热血了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳 没有小鸣的布偶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸣回家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 突然就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是只变化无常的小猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 面麻真的在仁碳身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给面麻实现愿望后 面麻不就消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么啦 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 到打工时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就要走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 面麻你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和波波一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说想留在这里 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就留在这里吧 尽情的留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闹得太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很高兴吧 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}哎 你看那个了？哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬季校服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}高中生用双节棍战斗的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初还以为是夏天的怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在已经换上冬装了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}少女在香港和僵尸战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 写上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厉害 好厉害啊 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只能用家里的这个本子写字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多写一些吧 再多聊一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}要聊什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 你…那个时候 那个…对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 对了 玩接龙游戏吧 画画接龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 那是什么？看起来像金楚糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双肩背包 弹珠 马里奥…奥…小手手和小手手的掌纹就是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}注释：日语假名接龙游戏 小手手和小手手的掌纹就是幸福是指你双手合十 幸福的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望远镜 开启
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即搜索 面麻队员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}您所拨打的电话暂时无人接听
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 接不上 打工开始了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么走得这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻只是在秘密基地而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么 我却这么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 小面麻她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我绝对不要面麻她消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对绝对不要叫仁碳死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是才死掉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 奇怪什么的 你自己才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 好啦 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 鲤鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲤鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小河里有一只超级大的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻啊 想更近的看一下 看啊 就在那呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在树根那里 游来游去的 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼哦 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳是赖皮虫嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一直一直待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就待 待在这里吧 我去替你抓鲤鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 仁碳 衣服会湿掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:20:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 笨蛋仁碳 会感冒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来呀 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:14.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}何ページも費やして　つづられた僕らの気分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:21.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}どうしてか一行の　空白を埋められない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:30.01,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}押花のしおり挟んで　君と転がす 使い捨ての自転車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:37.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}忘れかけのレンガを　積み上げた場所に行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:42.88,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}海を見渡す坂を駆け上って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}こわいくらいに青い空と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:55.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}右手にサイダー　左手はずっと君を探している
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:01:02.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}そうやって今は僕の方へ　問いつめることもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:09.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}まだ二人はすぐそこにいるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:17.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}どうかまたあえますようになんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:26.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}どうかしてるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:14.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}填寫了好幾頁 我們那連綿的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:21.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}卻為何填補不了那空白的一行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:30.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}夾上乾花瓣做的書籤 與你共騎上那丟棄的自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:37.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}前往已遺忘的卻堆滿回憶的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:42.88,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}登上遠望海景的坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}藍得刺眼的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:55.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}右手拿著汽水 左手一直追尋著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:01:02.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}現在已沒有需要向我詢問的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:09.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}明明兩人近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:17.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}卻祈望終有一日能相見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:26.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}這是為何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:27.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}君と夏の終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:32.50,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}将来の梦 大きな希望 忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:39.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}10年后の8月 また出会えるのを 信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:47.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}最高の思い出を…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:55.99,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}出会いはふっとした瞬間 帰り道の交差点で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:22:02.49,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}声をかけてくれたね  "一緒に帰ろう"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:09.99,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}嬉しくって 楽しくって 冒険も いろいろしたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:17.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}二人の 秘密の 基地の中
